    <p>Mr. ANJEM CHOUDARY (Islam4UK): We are obviously having a procession. Its in Wootton Bassett. Thats correct. But its not about the people there. Its not against them personally. Rather, its to highlight the real cost of the war in Afghanistan. </p>
