    <p>RENEE MONTAGNE, host: </p>
    <p>Returning to the story of Nidal Hasan, the U.S. Army Major charged in last years Fort Hood shooting, NPR has learned the Army has told some of the psychiatrists supervising Hasan at Walter Reed Hospital that it's investigating them  and they may face punishment. </p>
