    <p>GARCIA-NAVARRO: I'm extremely upset when I think of the settlements, because settlements are an impediment to the establishment of an independent Palestine. But I dont think anyone is serious about us getting a state, he says. They are laughing at us, he says. The Israelis are laughing at us. </p>
    <p>Mr. RAOUL: (Foreign language spoken) </p>
    <p>GARCIA-NAVARRO: But still, he says, he will continue to work in the settlements for as long as he can. </p>
